---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Public Records Request | Town of Littleton, NH" description="Submit a Right to Know request under New Hampshire RSA 91-A to access public government records.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-light-blue py-16" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-6">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-body-text list-none p-0 m-0">
          <li>
            <a href="/services" class="hover:underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:ring-offset-2 rounded">
              Services
            </a>
          </li>
          <li aria-hidden="true">/</li>
          <li aria-current="page" class="text-navy font-medium">Public Records Request</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Public Records Request</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-body-text mb-6 max-w-2xl">
        Submit a Right to Know request under New Hampshire RSA 91-A to access public government records.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-body-text">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mid-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Town Clerk</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mid-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
          </svg>
          <a href="tel:+16035550101" class="underline hover:no-underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:ring-offset-2 rounded">
            (603) 555-0101
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mid-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
          <a href="mailto:clerk@littletonnh.gov" class="underline hover:no-underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:ring-offset-2 rounded">
            clerk@littletonnh.gov
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is RSA 91-A -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white" aria-labelledby="rsa-heading">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 id="rsa-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6 text-center">New Hampshire Right to Know Law</h2>
      <div class="text-body-text space-y-4">
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          New Hampshire's Right to Know Law (RSA 91-A) is one of the strongest public records laws in the nation. It ensures that the actions of government are conducted openly, and that public records are available for inspection by any person. This law reflects the fundamental principle that government exists to serve its citizens and should operate transparently.
        </p>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          Under RSA 91-A, citizens have the right to access governmental records, attend public meetings, and review minutes of those meetings. The Town of Littleton is committed to honoring both the letter and spirit of this important law, and we strive to make the records request process as straightforward as possible.
        </p>
        <p class="pt-2">
          <a
            href="https://www.sos.nh.gov/administration/right-know"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-navy font-semibold underline hover:no-underline focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:ring-offset-2 rounded"
            aria-label="Learn more about RSA 91-A at sos.nh.gov (opens in new tab)"
          >
            Learn more at sos.nh.gov <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How to Submit -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-light-blue" aria-labelledby="submit-steps-heading">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
      <h2 id="submit-steps-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">How to Submit a Request</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <!-- Fixed: navy on white passes contrast — was text-gold which failed -->
        <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Identify Records</h3>
        <p class="text-body-text">Describe the records you are seeking as specifically as possible.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Submit Request</h3>
        <p class="text-body-text">Submit in writing by email, mail, or in person to the Town Clerk's office.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Town Reviews</h3>
        <p class="text-body-text">The town has 5 business days to respond to your request.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="step-number" aria-hidden="true">4</div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Receive Records</h3>
        <p class="text-body-text">Records are provided in the format requested when possible.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Submit Form -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white" aria-labelledby="form-heading">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 id="form-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-8 text-center">Submit Your Request</h2>
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm text-body-text mb-6">
          <span aria-hidden="true">*</span> Required field
        </p>
        <form action="#" method="post" novalidate class="space-y-6">

          <div>
            <label for="full-name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">
              Full Name <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-red-700">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="full-name"
              name="full-name"
              required
              aria-required="true"
              autocomplete="name"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">
              Email Address <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-red-700">*</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              required
              aria-required="true"
              autocomplete="email"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">
              Phone Number <span class="font-normal text-body-text">(optional)</span>
            </label>
            <input
              type="tel"
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              autocomplete="tel"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="records-requested" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">
              Records Requested <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-red-700">*</span>
            </label>
            <textarea
              id="records-requested"
              name="records-requested"
              rows="5"
              required
              aria-required="true"
              placeholder="Please describe the records you are seeking as specifically as possible..."
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:border-transparent resize-y"
            ></textarea>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="preferred-format" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">
              Preferred Format
            </label>
            <select
              id="preferred-format"
              name="preferred-format"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:border-transparent bg-white"
            >
              <option value="electronic">Electronic</option>
              <option value="paper">Paper</option>
              <option value="either">Either</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-navy text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-navy focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Submit Request
          </button>

        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-light-blue" aria-labelledby="expect-heading">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 text-center">
      <h2 id="expect-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">What to Expect</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="expect-grid">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-4">Response Timeline</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-body-text list-none p-0 m-0">
          {[
            '5 business days to acknowledge your request',
            'Records provided promptly after review',
            'Complex requests may take longer to fulfill',
            'You will be notified of any delays',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mid-blue mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-4">Fees</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-body-text list-none p-0 m-0">
          {[
            'First 15 minutes of search: free',
            'After 15 minutes: $25/hour',
            'Copies: $0.10 per page',
            'Electronic records: often free',
          ].map((item) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mid-blue mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
              </svg>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-body-text mt-4 italic">
          Fee waivers may be requested for public interest purposes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Exemptions -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white" aria-labelledby="exemptions-heading">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 id="exemptions-heading" class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy mb-6 text-center">Common Exemptions</h2>
      <div class="text-body-text space-y-4">
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          While New Hampshire's Right to Know Law provides broad access to government records, certain categories of information are exempt from disclosure to protect privacy, public safety, and other important interests. If any portion of your request falls under an exemption, we will provide the non-exempt portions and explain which exemption applies.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-navy">Common exemptions under RSA 91-A include:</p>
        <ul class="exemptions-list">
          <li>Personnel and medical files of employees</li>
          <li>Ongoing criminal investigation records</li>
          <li>Internal personnel practices and procedures</li>
          <li>Attorney-client privileged communications</li>
          <li>Confidential commercial or financial information</li>
          <li>Records related to emergency response plans</li>
          <li>Student records protected by FERPA</li>
          <li>Information that would constitute an invasion of privacy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .steps-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Fixed: navy on white passes contrast — was text-gold on white which failed */
  .step-number {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1B2E4B;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .expect-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .expect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .exemptions-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: #1E2D3D;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .exemptions-list li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
</style>